OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FItalian PM sues Placebo    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffrontman for defamation    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Italian Prime Minister Giorgia Meloni  
OL,6, is suing Placebo singer Brian Molko for
OL,7, defamation after he launched into a    
OL,8, rant against her during a gig in Turin 
OL,9, last month, Italian media report.      
OL,11,FMr Molko called Ms Meloni a fascist and
OL,12,Fa racist from the stage of the Sonic   
OL,13,FPark festival.                         
OL,15,FProsecutors in Turin opened an         
OL,16,Finvestigation into Mr Molko soon after.
OL,18,FMs Meloni has not commented publicly   
OL,19,Fabout the issue although the BBC has   
OL,20,Fapproached her team for a reaction.    
